public class DojoContentPane
extends AbstractDojoComplexPane

Class of DOJO panels that present only the feature that this to gather widgets (Dojo of other). These panels are useful when some widgets created from DOJO know only manipulate DOJO widget. (as the Toggler, TaskBar for example).

This component is an encapsulation GWT of Dojo components. Warning the widget exist under 3 faces :

  • a GWT widget (this!)
  • a Dojo widget (which play the role of 'this' for GWT)
  • a structur of DOM elements, the only exploitable presentation by the navigator.

Author:
Henry, Vianney
